data.description: Welcome home to 1025 Blue Beech Ln in the charming community of Kingsland Heights! This lovely 1 story home offers a convenient location just off of I-10 & is zoned to the highly acclaimed Katy ISD. Step inside to discover an open floor plan concept, with vinyl flooring throughout the main walking areas. The spacious 3 bedrooms & 2 full baths provide ample space for comfortable living. The master suite features a walk-in shower & a large walk-in closet. Recessed lighting adds a touch of elegance throughout the home. The kitchen boasts vinyl flooring, dark cabinetry, stainless steel appliances, & a giant kitchen island perfect for bar seating. The family room is cozy & inviting, with carpet & plenty of natural sunlight streaming in through the large windows. This open concept layout is ideal for hosting family & friends during the holidays & those summer days! Motivated seller, appliances are staying! Don't miss the opportunity to make this your dream home - schedule your showing today!
